{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":935,"text":"Today I am going to teach you"},{"time":3049,"text":"how to play my favorite game:"},{"time":6809,"text":"massively multiplayer thumb-wrestling."},{"time":10292,"text":"It's the only game in the world that I know of"},{"time":13612,"text":"that allows you, the player,"},{"time":15679,"text":"the opportunity to experience"},{"time":18098,"text":"10 positive emotions in 60 seconds or less."},{"time":22486,"text":"This is true, so if you play this game with me today"},{"time":24998,"text":"for just one single minute,"},{"time":27001,"text":"you will get to feel joy, relief, love, surprise,"},{"time":30701,"text":"pride, curiosity, excitement, awe and wonder,"},{"time":33767,"text":"contentment, and creativity,"},{"time":35365,"text":"all in the span of one minute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36904,"text":"So this sounds pretty good, right?\nNow you're willing to play."},{"time":39236,"text":"In order to teach you this game,"},{"time":40799,"text":"I'm going to need some volunteers"},{"time":42172,"text":"to come up onstage really quickly,"},{"time":44075,"text":"and we're going to do a little hands-on demo."},{"time":45553,"text":"While they're coming up, I should let you know,"},{"time":47594,"text":"this game was invented 10 years ago"},{"time":50056,"text":"by an artists' collective in Austria named Monochrom."},{"time":53353,"text":"So thank you, Monochrom."},{"time":55098,"text":"Okay, so most people are familiar"},{"time":57141,"text":"with traditional, two-person thumb-wrestling."},{"time":59133,"text":"Sunni, let's just remind them."},{"time":60721,"text":"One, two, three, four, \nI declare a thumb war, and we wrestle,"},{"time":63507,"text":"and of course Sunni beats me\nbecause she's the best."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65607,"text":"Now the first thing about\nmassively multiplayer thumb-wrestling,"},{"time":69411,"text":"we're the gamer generation."},{"time":70822,"text":"There are a billion gamers on the planet now,"},{"time":73173,"text":"so we need more of a challenge."},{"time":74727,"text":"So the first thing we need is more thumbs."},{"time":78106,"text":"So Eric, come on over."},{"time":79800,"text":"So we could get three thumbs together,"},{"time":82611,"text":"and Peter could join us."},{"time":85069,"text":"We could even have four thumbs together,"},{"time":86789,"text":"and the way you win"},{"time":88316,"text":"is you're the first person\nto pin someone else's thumb."},{"time":91513,"text":"This is really important. You can't, like,"},{"time":93371,"text":"wait while they fight it out and\nthen swoop in at the last minute."},{"time":95908,"text":"That is not how you win."},{"time":97403,"text":"Ah, who did that? Eric you did that."},{"time":98738,"text":"So Eric would have won. He was\nthe first person to pin my thumb."},{"time":101540,"text":"Okay, so that's the first rule,"},{"time":102950,"text":"and we can see that three or four"},{"time":104809,"text":"is kind of the typical number of thumbs in a node,"},{"time":107988,"text":"but if you feel ambitious,\nyou don't have to hold back."},{"time":110630,"text":"We can really go for it."},{"time":111995,"text":"So you can see up here."},{"time":114161,"text":"Now the only other rule you need to remember is,"},{"time":117133,"text":"gamer generation, we like a challenge."},{"time":119400,"text":"I happen to notice you all have"},{"time":121047,"text":"some thumbs you're not using."},{"time":122883,"text":"So I think we should kind of get some more involved."},{"time":125890,"text":"And if we had just four people,"},{"time":127660,"text":"we would do it just like this,"},{"time":129498,"text":"and we would try and wrestle"},{"time":131184,"text":"both thumbs at the same time."},{"time":132965,"text":"Perfect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134272,"text":"Now, if we had more people in the room,"},{"time":136386,"text":"instead of just wrestling in a closed node,"},{"time":138265,"text":"we might reach out and try\nand grab some other people."},{"time":141048,"text":"And in fact, that's what we're going to do right now."},{"time":142769,"text":"We're going to try and get all, something like,"},{"time":145321,"text":"I don't know, 1,500 thumbs in this room"},{"time":148297,"text":"connected in a single node."},{"time":149610,"text":"And we have to connect both levels,"},{"time":152650,"text":"so if you're up there, you're going to be"},{"time":155096,"text":"reaching down and reaching up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157309,"text":"Now — (Laughter) —"},{"time":158983,"text":"before we get started --"},{"time":160875,"text":"This is great. You're excited to play. —"},{"time":163908,"text":"before we get started, can I have\nthe slides back up here really quick,"},{"time":166988,"text":"because if you get good at this game,"},{"time":168945,"text":"I want you to know there are some advanced levels."},{"time":171581,"text":"So this is the kind of simple level, right?"},{"time":174493,"text":"But there are advanced configurations."},{"time":176405,"text":"This is called the Death Star Configuration."},{"time":178415,"text":"Any Star Wars fans?"},{"time":180122,"text":"And this one's called the Möbius Strip."},{"time":182470,"text":"Any science geeks, you get that one."},{"time":184290,"text":"This is the hardest level. This is the extreme."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187194,"text":"So we'll stick with the normal one for now,"},{"time":189208,"text":"and I'm going to give you 30 seconds,"},{"time":191150,"text":"every thumb into the node,"},{"time":193175,"text":"connect the upper and the lower levels,"},{"time":194648,"text":"you guys go on down there."},{"time":196150,"text":"Thirty seconds. Into the network. Make the node."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201178,"text":"Stand up! It's easier if you stand up."},{"time":203932,"text":"Everybody, up up up up up!"},{"time":207871,"text":"Stand up, my friends."},{"time":211161,"text":"All right."},{"time":212193,"text":"Don't start wrestling yet."},{"time":215001,"text":"If you have a free thumb, wave it around,"},{"time":217781,"text":"make sure it gets connected."},{"time":221002,"text":"Okay. We need to do a last-minute thumb check."},{"time":223694,"text":"If you have a free thumb,\nwave it around to make sure."},{"time":227027,"text":"Grab that thumb!"},{"time":228520,"text":"Reach behind you. There you go."},{"time":229863,"text":"Any other thumbs?"},{"time":231421,"text":"Okay, on the count of three, you're going to go."},{"time":233936,"text":"Try to keep track. Grab, grab, grab it."},{"time":236649,"text":"Okay? One, two, three, go!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239179,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":246520,"text":"Did you win? You got it? You got it? Excellent!"},{"time":249532,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":252049,"text":"Well done. Thank you. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255591,"text":"All right."},{"time":256996,"text":"While you are basking in the glow"},{"time":260408,"text":"of having won your first"},{"time":262210,"text":"massively multiplayer thumb-wrestling game,"},{"time":263825,"text":"let's do a quick recap on the positive emotions."},{"time":266415,"text":"So curiosity."},{"time":268354,"text":"I said \"massively multiplayer thumb-wrestling.\""},{"time":270326,"text":"You were like, \"What the hell is she talking about?\""},{"time":272126,"text":"So I provoked a little curiosity."},{"time":274003,"text":"Creativity: it took creativity to solve the problem"},{"time":276672,"text":"of getting all the thumbs into the node."},{"time":278031,"text":"I'm reaching around and I'm reaching up."},{"time":279444,"text":"So you used creativity. That was great."},{"time":280998,"text":"How about surprise? The actual feeling"},{"time":283250,"text":"of trying to wrestle two thumbs at once\nis pretty surprising."},{"time":285912,"text":"You heard that sound go up in the room."},{"time":287772,"text":"We had excitement. As you started to wrestle,"},{"time":289611,"text":"maybe you're starting to win\nor this person's, like, really into it,"},{"time":291816,"text":"so you kind of get the excitement going."},{"time":294302,"text":"We have relief. You got to stand up."},{"time":296245,"text":"You've been sitting for awhile, so the physical relief,"},{"time":298003,"text":"getting to shake it out."},{"time":299320,"text":"We had joy. You were laughing, smiling.\nLook at your faces. This room is full of joy."},{"time":303880,"text":"We had some contentment."},{"time":305840,"text":"I didn't see anybody sending text messages\nor checking their email while we were playing,"},{"time":309529,"text":"so you were totally content to be playing."},{"time":311522,"text":"The most important three emotions,"},{"time":313210,"text":"awe and wonder, we had everybody\nconnected physically for a minute."},{"time":316822,"text":"When was the last time you were at TED"},{"time":318421,"text":"and you got to connect physically\nwith every single person in the room?"},{"time":321250,"text":"And it's truly awesome and wondrous."},{"time":322896,"text":"And speaking of physical connection,"},{"time":324740,"text":"you guys know I love the hormone oxytocin,"},{"time":327743,"text":"you release oxytocin, you feel bonded\nto everyone in the room."},{"time":330920,"text":"You guys know that the best way\nto release oxytocin quickly"},{"time":333436,"text":"is to hold someone else's hand\nfor at least six seconds."},{"time":335935,"text":"You guys were all holding hands\nfor way more than six seconds,"},{"time":338487,"text":"so we are all now biochemically primed"},{"time":340267,"text":"to love each other. That is great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342120,"text":"And the last emotion of pride."},{"time":345044,"text":"How many people are like me. Just admit it."},{"time":347848,"text":"You lost both your thumbs."},{"time":348994,"text":"It just didn't work out for you."},{"time":350943,"text":"That's okay, because you learned a new skill today."},{"time":353506,"text":"You learned, from scratch,\na game you never knew before."},{"time":356270,"text":"Now you know how to play it.\nYou can teach other people."},{"time":357976,"text":"So congratulations."},{"time":359544,"text":"How many of you won just won thumb?"},{"time":361865,"text":"All right. I have very good news for you."},{"time":363236,"text":"According to the official rules"},{"time":364368,"text":"of massively multiplayer thumb-wrestling,"},{"time":366364,"text":"this makes you a grandmaster of the game."},{"time":370145,"text":"Because there aren't that many\npeople who know how to play,"},{"time":372377,"text":"we have to kind of accelerate the program"},{"time":374576,"text":"more than a game like chess."},{"time":376169,"text":"So congratulations, grandmasters."},{"time":377962,"text":"Win one thumb once, you will\nbecome a grandmaster."},{"time":380453,"text":"Did anybody win both their thumbs?"},{"time":382482,"text":"Yes. Awesome. Okay."},{"time":383981,"text":"Get ready to update your Twitter or Facebook status."},{"time":386904,"text":"You guys, according to the rules,"},{"time":388670,"text":"are legendary grandmasters, so congratulations."},{"time":392346,"text":"I will just leave you with this tip,\nif you want to play again."},{"time":395075,"text":"The best way to become a legendary grandmaster,"},{"time":396863,"text":"you've got your two nodes going on."},{"time":398949,"text":"Pick off the one that looks easiest."},{"time":400671,"text":"They're not paying attention. They look kind of weak."},{"time":402652,"text":"Focus on that one and do something crazy"},{"time":404736,"text":"with this arm."},{"time":406072,"text":"As soon as you win, suddenly stop."},{"time":408401,"text":"Everybody is thrown off. You go in for the kill."},{"time":410201,"text":"That's how you become a legendary grandmaster\nof massively multiplayer thumb-wrestling."},{"time":412767,"text":"Thank you for letting me\nteach you my favorite game."},{"time":415294,"text":"Wooo! (Applause)"},{"time":417130,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}